<lb n="0858c18"/><head type="no">No. 1346 [No. 1347]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0858c19"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0858005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>諸佛集會陀羅尼<note n="0858006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（與趙宋施護所出息除中夭經同本）十四字夾註【元】【明】，但明本無本字</note><note n="0858006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＋（與趙宋施護所出息除中夭經同本）十四字夾註【元】，＋（與趙宋施護所出息除中夭經同）十三字夾註【明】</note><app n="0858006"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">經<note place="inline">與趙宋施護所出息除中夭經同本</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">經<note place="inline">與趙宋施護所出息除中夭經同</note></rdg></app><note n="0858007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】</note><note n="0858007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0858007"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0858c20"/>
<lb n="0858c21"/><byline type="Translator">唐三藏法師提雲般若等奉　制譯</byline>
<lb n="0858c22"/><p>如是我聞。一時佛在&M010527;伽河邊。護世四天王
<lb n="0858c23"/>之所圍繞。爾時世尊告毘沙門等四天王言。
<lb n="0858c24"/>汝等當知一切眾生。若男若女若長若幼。皆
<lb n="0858c25"/>為四種大怖所纏。謂生老病死。然於其中死
<lb n="0858c26"/>怖一種最難除遣。我今為汝說除遣法</p>
<lb n="0858c27"/><p>爾時四天王即從座起。合掌恭敬白佛言。世
<lb n="0858c28"/>尊我等今者獲大善利。得值如來攝受世間
<lb n="0858c29"/>施其命故</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1346.0859a" n="0859a"/>
<lb n="0859a01"/><p>爾時世尊從座而起。面于東方彈指唱言。彼
<lb n="0859a02"/>方所有諸佛如來應正等覺。莫不皆為一切
<lb n="0859a03"/>眾生。而成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。諸佛當知
<lb n="0859a04"/>我今為欲哀愍救護諸眾生故。轉先未轉第
<lb n="0859a05"/>二法輪。當令眾生色力壽命皆悉增長。永復
<lb n="0859a06"/>無有非時<note n="0859001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夭＝犮【宋】＊</note><app n="0859001"><lem>夭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">犮</rdg></app>橫。唯願諸佛來此會中。為護眾
<lb n="0859a07"/>生共以威神除其橫苦。南西北方四維上下
<lb n="0859a08"/>皆亦如是。是時如來以佛眼觀十方世界。一
<lb n="0859a09"/>一世界皆有諸佛。<note n="0859002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">側＝&CB03203;【元】【明】</note><app n="0859002"><lem>側</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB03203;</rdg></app>塞充滿猶如稻麻。悉來
<lb n="0859a10"/>此會而為等侶。然見十方一切世界。一一方
<lb n="0859a11"/>處諸佛世尊亦皆遍滿分明顯現。如是一切
<lb n="0859a12"/>諸佛如來。俱時發聲而說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0859a13"/><p type="dharani">折禮<note place="inline"><note n="0859003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔句〕－【明】＊</note><app n="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一</note>折羅折禮<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>二</note>毘那<note place="inline"><note n="0859004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【三】</note><note n="0859004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔去〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859004"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>借音即此字之上聲下<note n="0859005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【三】</note><note n="0859005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859005"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>字傍註
<lb n="0859a14"/>上<note n="0859006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">字＝去者【三】</note><note n="0859006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">字＝去者【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859006"><lem>字</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">去者</rdg></app>皆倣此</note>徵<note place="inline">珍里<note n="0859007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】＊</note><app n="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>三</note>莎<note place="inline">蘇括<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>悉底<note place="inline">都以<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>下同</note>雞<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>四</note>斫
<lb n="0859a15"/>迦爛揭時<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>五</note>&CB00425;羅舍漫都<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>六</note>薩婆嚕<note place="inline">依魯字本
<lb n="0859a16"/>音而轉舌呼之其下口邊作<note n="0859008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（梨）＋犁【宋】【元】，（犁）＋犁【明】</note><app n="0859008"><lem>犁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">梨犁</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">犁犁</rdg></app>羅麗皆倣此</note>伽<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>七</note>阿那<note place="inline"><note n="0859009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>&CB00600;<note place="inline">卓諧<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>八</note>俱
<lb n="0859a17"/>那<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>&CB00600;<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>九</note>摩訶捺&CB00600;<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十</note>折&CB02740;折&CB02740;<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十一</note>
<lb n="0859a18"/>醯<note place="inline">呼計<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>下同</note>摩具&CB00074;<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十二</note>醯摩&CB00135;產<note place="inline"><note n="0859010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0859010"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>地<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十三</note>
<lb n="0859a19"/>醯摩室<note n="0859011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尼＝尸【宋】【元】</note><app n="0859011"><lem>尼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">尸</rdg></app><note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十四</note>吉囉<note n="0859012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【三】</note><note n="0859012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔上〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859012"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>陛<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十五</note>吉囉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>鞞<note place="inline">句十
<lb n="0859a20"/>六</note>醯<note place="inline">引聲</note>俱囉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>&CB02740;<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十七</note>俱囉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note><note n="0859013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02740;＝&CB00074;【三】</note><note n="0859013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02740;＝&CB00074;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859013"><lem>&CB02740;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00074;</rdg></app><note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>十八</note>俱
<lb n="0859a21"/>末底<note place="inline">句十九</note>毘奢麼<note place="inline">謀跛<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>泥<note place="inline">句二十</note>戍暑<note place="inline">輸矩<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>毘<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0859a22"/>婆<note place="inline">句二十一</note>阿折禮毘折禮<note place="inline">句二十二</note>摩毘<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>濫婆<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>二十三</note>
<lb n="0859a23"/>呼<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859010"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>牟呼<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859010"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>牟<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>二十四</note></p>
<lb n="0859a24"/><p>爾時十方諸佛。一一皆有金剛密跡王親近
<lb n="0859a25"/>圍繞。此無量金剛王眾。復共同聲而說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0859a26"/><p type="dharani">&CB03837;<note place="inline">呼濫<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>引聲<app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>一</note>&CB03837;<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>二</note>室勢<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>三</note>颯婆<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859010"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>訶
<lb n="0859a27"/><note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>四</note></p>
<lb n="0859a28"/><p>爾時毘沙門天王白佛言世尊。我今亦為擁
<lb n="0859a29"/>護眾生說陀羅尼。令其無有非時<app type="＊" source="0859001"><lem>夭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">犮</rdg></app>橫。唯願
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1346.0859b" n="0859b"/>
<lb n="0859b01"/>如來垂哀與力。即說&CB00057;曰</p><p type="dharani" place="inline">稅低<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>一</note>稅怛
<lb n="0859b02"/>犁<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>二</note>履梨<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>三</note></p>
<lb n="0859b03"/><p>爾時毘盧勒叉天王亦作是言。我今為欲護
<lb n="0859b04"/>諸眾生說陀羅尼。即說&CB00057;曰</p><p type="dharani" place="inline">摩蹬耆<note place="inline">瞿雞<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>一</note>
<lb n="0859b05"/>摩蹬耆<note place="inline"><note n="0859014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祇＝都【宋】，祁【元】【明】</note><note n="0859014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祇＝都【宋】，＝祁【元】【明】</note><app n="0859014"><lem>祇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">都</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">祁</rdg></app>里<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>尼<note place="inline">&CB00135;咨<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>二</note>暑<note place="inline">輸矩<app type="＊" source="0859007"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>下同</note>摩暑母<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0859b06"/>三</note></p>
<lb n="0859b07"/><p>爾時提頭賴吒天王。亦為擁護諸眾生故而
<lb n="0859b08"/>說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0859b09"/><p type="dharani">折&CB00691;折&CB00691;颯婆<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859010"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>訶</p>
<lb n="0859b10"/><p>爾時毘樓博叉天王亦說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0859b11"/><p type="dharani">跋凌<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859010"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>婆<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0859009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>婆</p>
<lb n="0859b12"/><p>爾時世尊告四天王言諸天等此陀羅尼。從
<lb n="0859b13"/>於一切諸佛所生。一切諸佛共所知見。若善
<lb n="0859b14"/>男子善女人。乃至有能一日之中讀一遍者。
<lb n="0859b15"/>是人終不墮於惡趣。當於是人起大師想。若
<lb n="0859b16"/>有人為欲利益一切眾生。於日日中讀誦斯
<lb n="0859b17"/>&CB00057;。能令眾生壽命增長。亦令其人災橫怖畏
<lb n="0859b18"/><note n="0859015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝並【三】</note><note n="0859015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆＝並【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859015"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">並</rdg></app>得消除。無諸惡相及眾<note n="0859016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疾＝病【三】</note><note n="0859016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">疾＝病【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859016"><lem>疾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">病</rdg></app>苦。水不能漂
<lb n="0859b19"/>火不能燒。刀不能傷毒不能害。若在在處處
<lb n="0859b20"/>有能讀誦此陀羅尼。當知此處則為十方一切
<lb n="0859b21"/>諸佛常所護念。若人自書若教人書。其人則
<lb n="0859b22"/>為承事供養一切諸佛。何以故。若於眾生能
<lb n="0859b23"/>作饒益。則為供養一切佛故。若有專欲擁護
<lb n="0859b24"/>其身。當書此&CB00057;佩著身上。若所在之處有深
<lb n="0859b25"/>信法善男子善女人等。或遇災難欲令除滅。
<lb n="0859b26"/>疾應如法受持此&CB00057;。持&CB00057;法著。先當<note n="0859017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">簡＝揀【三】</note><note n="0859017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">簡＝揀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859017"><lem>簡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">揀</rdg></app>擇清
<lb n="0859b27"/>淨之處。以栴檀末而塗其地。成一方壇縱廣
<lb n="0859b28"/>七肘。其人應從月初八日。香湯洗浴著新淨
<lb n="0859b29"/>衣受八戒齋。唯食粳米石蜜牛乳。取黑沈香
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1346.0859c" n="0859c"/>
<lb n="0859c01"/>及龍腦香。共滿一兩置於壇上。又取白檀香
<lb n="0859c02"/>或<note n="0859018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沆＝沈【三】</note><note n="0859018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沆＝沈【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0859018"><lem>沆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">沈</rdg></app>水香。或龍腦香或復丁香迦矩羅香。而
<lb n="0859c03"/>置於壇。其人誦此陀羅尼&CB00057;。&CB00057;此諸香。於日
<lb n="0859c04"/>日中皆七七遍滿于七日。至十五日一日不
<lb n="0859c05"/>食其日中時。以&CB00614;金香於其壇上作二十一
<lb n="0859c06"/>小壇。其一處中名如來壇。餘二十壇名金剛
<lb n="0859c07"/>王壇。又於壇外作四小壇。名四天王壇復取
<lb n="0859c08"/>麝香龍腦白檀&CB00614;金之香及紫檀末。於如來
<lb n="0859c09"/>壇若散若塗而為供養。自餘諸壇隨取一香
<lb n="0859c10"/>而供養之。又取乳酪<note n="0859019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝蘇【宋】</note><app n="0859019"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">蘇</rdg></app>及沙糖。如其次第以
<lb n="0859c11"/>新瓶四口。各別盛之置四天王壇上。又以淨
<lb n="0859c12"/>水著於瓶內。採十二種果樹之花而置其中。
<lb n="0859c13"/>又以香油然十支燈置如來壇。為欲供養十
<lb n="0859c14"/>方佛故。自餘諸壇各然一支。於前所&CB00057;諸香
<lb n="0859c15"/>之內。取龍腦及沈水。於如來壇而燒供養。其
<lb n="0859c16"/>餘壇上然自餘香。將然香時其如來壇及餘
<lb n="0859c17"/>壇香。復應各別誦此神&CB00057;而以&CB00057;之。若有眾
<lb n="0859c18"/>生得聞此香。非時夭橫靡不除滅。先所&CB00057;香
<lb n="0859c19"/>並燒盡已。然後收彼四天王食散於淨處</p>
<lb n="0859c20"/><p>佛說此經已。四大天王及一切世間天人阿
<lb n="0859c21"/>修羅乾闥婆等。歡喜奉行</p>
<lb n="0859c22"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>諸佛集會陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
